Name: Allen Mid Century Modern Tufted Genuine Leather Sofa in Cognac Tan
Description:
This comfortable living room couch will provide a fresh and pleasing look to your space and will be the center of attention thanks to its tufted design. This designer style top grain leather chesterfield sofas creates an inviting space for your guests or family entertainment activities.

Combining top-quality craftmanship and high-density foam, this set will provide you with great comfort and undoubtedly become the centerpiece of your living room, den, urban loft, condo. All pieces are made of top grain genuine leather and can be cleaned with a microfiber cloth.

Removable solid wood walnut color legs allow for simple delivery for tight spaces. Easy assembly, everyday use comfortable, affordable and durable quality leather couches.
Due to leather's natural characteristic, texture and color may vary.
